{"tid":488014,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭今次要follow習大大，趕絕低端人口！","createTime":"2017-12-03T10:04:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-03T13:29:37.000Z","uid":29314,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b4e6082ea6ba05ac3359d19bd057ddaff2f0fd11","tid":488014,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T10:04:59.000Z","msg":"據自由亞洲電台報道，河北、河南、山東、山西四省，加上天津及北京兩個直轄市，合共28個城市拒絕北京「低端人口」在當地開設「低端產業」，亦不接納他們在當地租房落戶。&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大批勞動階層被趕走，北京市亦漸漸出現問題。靠勞動階層撐起的電商、速遞及外賣及上網洗衣等服務，服務大部份都延遲或暫停。有在當地工作的外國人在網上表示，現時阿里巴巴的淘寶速遞要徵收額外的附加費。<br />\n<br />\n自由亞洲電台/《世界日報》"},{"pid":"acc3bfe99707b8fe642ab23676fbacf170b44252","tid":488014,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T10:09:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5919d709f3afd3f66f5a213b116eeb17ea8f81f3","tid":488014,"uid":13724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T10:10:35.000Z","msg":"不如將所有無物業嘅人趕走啦，我想睇吓到時啲有錢佬將層樓租俾邊個<br />\n<br />\n利申無香港樓"},{"pid":"8728cf7af9e51e55580c6077e7db6e3f691a0194","tid":488014,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T10:11:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不如將所有無物業嘅人趕走啦，我想睇吓到時啲有錢佬將層樓租俾邊個<br />\n<br />\n利申無香港樓</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05a2e9564353271ec7098d778dab43c70d4ad0fe","tid":488014,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T10:23:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>不如將所有無物業嘅人趕走啦，我想睇吓到時啲有錢佬將層樓租俾邊個<br />\n<br />\n利申無香港樓</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無樓但有交租IS OK。"},{"pid":"818e1b56607a93f42e88e03916aba4764f1a9059","tid":488014,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T10:30:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"665f1170f95d9cdba83deb3bbdfeb6f6c64fa260","tid":488014,"uid":76776,"li